features: LARGE CAPACITY: Our air fryer basket with baking paper for ovens offers a generous cooking space of 11.8 x 10 x 2.2 inches. Whether you're cooking french fries, bacon, vegetables, or cheese crackers, you can easily cook them all at once.

SAFE COOKING: The oven air fryer basket is made of high-quality food-grade 304 stainless steel, ensuring safety and compliance with FDA standards. The sturdy and heat-resistant stainless steel basket can be safely used at temperatures up to 450℉, providing long-lasting durability.

360° HEATING: Our air fryer basket for oven is designed with an ultra-fine mesh that evenly distributes heat, ensuring thorough cooking and eliminating excess fat. Enjoy your favorite fried foods without worrying about added calories and fat. This technology allows even conventional ovens to fry food using convection for healthier cooking and great taste.

EASY TO CLEAN: The stainless steel basket has a non-stick surface, making it easy to clean even if some food sticks to it. A quick soak will remove any residue. Additionally, the basket is dishwasher safe, making cleanup almost effortless and saving you time and effort.

MULTI-PURPOSE BAKING BASKET: Our air fryer pan is versatile and suitable for both commercial and home use. It's perfect for baking homemade pizzas, chicken, sandwiches, chips, and more. We offer 24-hour friendly service and a one-year warranty. If you encounter any issues with the product, please contact us promptly, and we will prioritize solving it for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I needed a way to “air fry” veggies in my convection oven
reviews.reviewText: It started with me using a small air fryer for veggies…and moved to me wanting to use my convection oven for preparing larger amounts of veggies. This air fryer basket enabled me to do a form of air frying two vegetable sides at once in my convection oven with great results. I used one of the included baking sheets to make for easy clean up and put the basket on a sheet pan to prevent oven drips. The basket seems sturdy and was easy to clean up. A good addition to my kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We got this to use as an oven pan rack because the old rack has worn out. While the size doesn't fit perfectly, it works well (although with a slight tilt). Our oven is also deep enough for this rack to sit on top of the oven rack, which is perfect for items like a frozen pizza with instructions to heat directly on an oven rack (without actually using the hard to wash oven rack).It also works on a cookie sheet to raise things off the bottom while in the oven -- another big win! And of course, it can also be a cooling rack outside the oven.We popped it in the dishwasher after it arrived and it looks great afterward -- sturdy and strong enough for most food items up to steaks and chicken leg quarters. A full size roast or whole chicken might be a bit much, but we have a different roasting pan and rack for that.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this thing!
reviews.reviewText: I was hoping this would fit into my air fryer oven but it didn't. I used it in my oven and loved how my crispy shrimp came out. The baking paper sheets that come with is awesome and makes clean up so easy. It is not much different than the basket that came with my air fryer, it cleans up easily. Even though it seems like a thin steel grid, it actually is pretty durable. I think this will work awesome in my fifth wheel oven. I love it and think it's a great purchase and decent price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect fit for my Cuisinart TOA-60 air fryer oven
reviews.reviewText: This rack is a perfect fit in my Cuisinart TOA-60 air fryer oven. It looks and feels the same as the OEM rack. Now, I can bake on both levels at the same time! It is sturdy, shiny, and glides perfectly in each rack position in my oven. The parchment sheets are a nice bonus!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great basket, works great. It even comes with perfectly sized parchment paper. It seems to be nonstick and I didn't do any research into that but it's a great basket. We used it in our oven with the convection setting. Which isn't exactly the same as air fryer but met our needs. The only reason I didn't give it 5 starts is because I don't know what materials are in the basket coating.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy air fryer basket
reviews.reviewText: This air fryer basket is very sturdy. There's a little height too so that you can use it on top of a cookie tray inside a regular oven to replicate a convection oven. I also flip it around and use it as a small cooling rack.
